These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: peas, zucchini
1. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Food   | peas | zucchini |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, disaster
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | disaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
